      "para_id": "Q000959.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Ningal , her lady , En-nirĝal-ana , en priestess of Nanna , ( Ur-Namma's ) beloved child , dedicated this ( stand/bowl ) for the well-being of Ur-Namma , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad , her father ."
    }
  ],
